{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>In <i>Stronghold Defenders</i>, your mission is not just survival\u2014it's the eradication of a creeping corruption threatening your stronghold.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every decision counts in this <strong>high-stakes battle</strong>, where the<strong> fall of your stronghold means defeat</strong>, but each attempt brings you closer to the ultimate goal of <strong>wiping out the corruption</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Blending the strategic depth of <strong>tower defense</strong> with <strong>rogue-lite</strong> progression, you'll <strong>gather resources</strong>, strategically place <strong>workers</strong>, <strong>build</strong> and <strong>upgrade</strong> powerful <strong>defense towers</strong>, and push deeper into corrupted lands.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Rich Resource Management: </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather and balance several resources, each with their own purposes.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003360/extras/steam_resources.png?t=1730977364\" />  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Accords System:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make crucial strategic decisions through the <strong>Accords</strong>, offering unique choices that shape your gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003360/extras/SD_Accords.png?t=1730977364\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dynamic Tower Defense Mechanics:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Construct and upgrade a variety of <strong>defense towers</strong>, each with <strong>unique traits</strong> and <strong>branching enhancement</strong> possibilities to achieve different <strong>synergies.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003360/extras/SD_Upgrades.png?t=1730977364\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Strategic Worker Allocation:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Assign</strong> them strategically to <strong>gather</strong> resources, <strong>enhance your defenses</strong> or send them out into the world to complete <strong>objectives</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003360/extras/SD_Workers.png?t=1730977364\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Roguelite Tech Tree Progression:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock new <strong>buildings</strong>, powerful <strong>upgrades</strong>, and <strong>world-altering features</strong> through the\u00a0<strong>Tech Tree</strong>, making each game session <strong>unique</strong> and <strong>rewarding</strong> as you grow stronger and discover new possibilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003360/extras/SD_Tech_Tree.png?t=1730977364\" /></p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome to Stronghold Defenders!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3003360/d4e3d12c4cb3eaf69884917689652aaa55d8dcf1.jpg"},{"name":"Corruption Defeated","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3003360/bec75c6ea5c1ac4b62539f41b21e7e643fedd634.jpg"},{"name":"Sky-High Morale","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3003360/e7f29a5b29c8db53e445e43d68fa6e4125f8127e.jpg"},{"name":"Skill Master","path":"https://cdn.akam